PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AUTHORIZING FEDERAL EMPLOYEES TO ACQUIRE INTERESTS IN CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (ORDER NO. 2, 1998) which authorizes Norman Lee McCowan, of Hay River, N.W.T., to lease the whole of an unsurveyed piece of land (0.54 hectares) situate near kilometre 4.4 of N.W.T.
